2005-06-30  Janne Jalkanen  <Janne.Jalkanen@ecyrd.com>

        * 2.3.3

        * Mass merge of JSPWIKI_ARJ_BRANCH
        
        * Added Andrew Jaquith's authentication code, replacing the
        old system completely.  This is likely to break everything.
