        full XHTML :-).

        * Several small bugfixes: ([[ not working, single {'s getting
        destroyed, etc.)

        * Removed clear=all from HR, added \\\ to do a <br clear=all>.  HR
        looked quite odd.

        * ":" after the first no longer breaks description lists.        

